data.description: Here's your chance to become the owner of this nicely maintained home with a two car detached garage that is fully electric. Perfect for a first time home buyer or just looking to downsize. Upon entering the home from the covered deck, you will walk into the mud room that includes main floor laundry and plenty of pantry storage. The remainder of the first floor consists of a nice size living room and large eat-in kitchen. On the second floor you will find the full bathroom, two large bedrooms, a walk in cedar closet and a smaller room that could be used as a nursery or a large walk in closet. This home comes with central air conditioning, 200 amp service, newer windows and shingles that were installed 10 years ago. Don't wait! Call today to schedule your very own private showing
